column5: What does it mean to be a guide?? And how do you become one???

Keep on posting reports, or replying to other members' posts, until you reach 500, or invest in a 22 to 30 something foot boat, get to know a Lake and where there are fish to be caught on a consistent, I mean consistent basis, have an advertising budget, and....voila, you too can be a guide. See, it isn't that big of a deal.  (at least the first part).
Ok lets meet up. Show me the ropes.  j/k   Congrats dsn
